text: Notre-Dame-de-la-Mer is a commune. It is in Île-de-France in the Yvelines department in north-central France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2019 and consists of the former communes of Jeufosse (the seat) and Port- Villez.Arrêté préfectoral 27 September 2018 == References == Category:2019 establishments in France Category:Communes in Yvelines
title: Notre-Dame-de-la-Mer
